NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Section::BashCompletion::GetoptLongComplete - Add a BASH
    COMPLETION section for Getopt::Long::Complete-based scripts

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Pod::Weaver::Section::BashCompletion::GetoptLongComplete (from Perl
    distribution Pod-Weaver-Section-BashCompletion-GetoptLongComplete),
    released on 2014-11-12.

SYNOPSIS
    In your "weaver.ini":

     [BashCompletion::GetoptLongComplete]

DESCRIPTION
    This section plugin adds a BASH COMPLETION section for
    Getopt::Long::Complete-based scripts. The section contains information
    on how to activate bash completion for the scripts.

SEE ALSO
    Getopt::Long::Complete

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Pod-Weaver-Section-BashCompletion-GetoptLo
    ngComplete>.

